Ruby installation..

rvm install
rvm list
rvm use version_name
rvm install ruby-(version_name)
ruby -v



for installing rail framework:

gem install rails
bundle install
rails -v

rails c    (open console)
rails s -p 3001(open local server)

creating pjoct_name in framework:
rails new airline_management_system                                          

for delete project:
rm -r project_name

creating pjoct_name in framework:(databse: mysql , oracle....etc.)
rails new project_name -d mysql

set username & password i n database.yml

rake db:create

rails g model model_name (creating model)

rails g controller controller_name (creating controller)

set route path for every methods of controller

start server (rails s -p 3001(open local server)
